      | Course 1 | C1        |
    And the following "course enrolments" exist:
      | user     | course | role           |
      | user1    | C1     | student        |
      | user2    | C1     | student        |
      | teacher  | C1     | editingteacher |
    And the following "core_payment > payment accounts" exist:
      | name           |
      | Account1       |
